      "rationale": "Iterative residuals reported (L2 < 1e-5 for momentum, 1e-6 for scalar) but solver error has not been formally bounded or compared to discretization error magnitude. Floating-point sensitivity study not performed. Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1."
    },
