      "acceptanceCriteria": "Statistical characterisation of test sample variability (hematocrit, donor variability, anticoagulant effects) provided; sample size justification documented.",
      "rationale": "Three independent blood donor samples used across five operating points. No statistical power analysis performed to justify sample size for MRL 5. Donor demographic data not reported. Factor flagged as epistemic gap. Achieved level 1."
