      "acceptanceCriteria": "Equivalency between validation experiment input parameters and COU simulation input parameters formally demonstrated; any non-equivalencies quantified and their impact on prediction credibility assessed.",
      "rationale": "No formal equivalency assessment has been performed between the FDA generic pump validation inputs and the proprietary VAD COU inputs. Geometric dissimilarity, speed range extrapolation, and fluid property differences are acknowledged in the validation report narrative but not quantified. Factor flagged as a critical epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1."
